nftsData.title: PKG#2624
nftsData.description: Proud Kitty Gang (aka PKG) consist of 6,666 dope kitty gangsters. Each Kitty is unique and randomly generated by programme based on more than 200 different traits. PKG is the family for all the special and proud kids in Web3. Tattooed Kitty Gang are our vanguard to Web3. Each Proud Kitty NFT gives you privilege to participate in exclusive activities in KittyVerse, such as winning bounty pool, receiving investment from PKG fund on the web3 project, wall-crossing to other metaverses, and so force.
